{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/wishlist.png?t=1727092163\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/ezgif-3-7712248edb.gif?t=1727092163\" /><strong>Drift, boost, and spin around corners at BLASTING SPEEDS in Project TurboBlast ,</strong>\u00a0a\u00a0Singleplayer + Multiplayer arcade-style racing game blending familiar drift handling of Kart racers and tight responsive controls of classic AG racing games. With a focus on being easy to pick up but difficult to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Project TURBOBLAST is my passion project  </strong>. It is a love letter and homage to old school arcade racing games like F-Zero, Hotwheels, CTR and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/ezgif-3-a84c0555d7.gif?t=1727092163\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLANNED FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Singleplayer Event Mode</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Multiple GameModes</strong> - Such as, but not limited to; <br>Survival <br>Score Attack<br>Time Attack<br>Knockout Race </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Time Trails, Ghost data + leaderboards</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Online+Lan Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Mod Support</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Vehicle Customization</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Driver Customization</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/JointheDiscord.png?t=1727092163\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAYTESTING AND SUPPORT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Want to get in on the racing early and offer feedback?</strong> Then you can join the discord! Link found in the &quot;links + info&quot; section along with other platforms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DONT FORGET TO WISHLIST THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wishlisting puts Project TURBOBLAST on the map for other people</strong> , and notifies you of news and demo releases! So it helps a ton, and is deeply appreciated &lt;3</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3148560?t=1727092163","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1727092163","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/24480806b6e3881ae95dfa3bbe05b976a834ba8a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727092163","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/24480806b6e3881ae95dfa3bbe05b976a834ba8a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727092163","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/wishlist.png?t=1727092163\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/ezgif-3-7712248edb.gif?t=1727092163\" /><strong>Drift, boost, and spin around corners at BLASTING SPEEDS in Project TurboBlast ,</strong>\u00a0a\u00a0Singleplayer + Multiplayer arcade-style racing game blending familiar drift handling of Kart racers 